Class SmackException.NoResponseException

    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    SmackException

    public static class SmackException.NoResponseException
extends SmackException
    Exception thrown always when there was no response to an request within the stanza(/packet) reply timeout of the used connection instance. You can modify (e.g. increase) the stanza(/packet) reply timeout with XMPPConnection.setPacketReplyTimeout(long).
    See Also:
